metadata.name: Waves from underwater by MK - Fiji #02
metadata.description:
フィジー諸島　ナギギア島　キングコングレフトにて2003年6月撮影

Photo taken at King Kong Left, Nagigia Island, Fiji Islands, June 2003
Swimming in the ocean with just a pair of flippers and a mask, using his intuitive sense to take photographs of waves from underwater.
